  "description": "The component that represents a table.\nA table is a set of tabular data. Line items can support data, images and actions.\n```html\n<fdp-table\n [dataSource]=\"source\"\n fdCompact\n selectionMode=\"multiple\"\n emptyTableMessage=\"No data found\">\n\n <fdp-table-toolbar\n  title=\"Order Line Items\"\n  [hideItemCount]=\"false\">\n </fdp-table-toolbar>\n\n <fdp-column\n  name=\"name\"\n  key=\"name\"\n  label=\"Name\"\n  align=\"start\">\n </fdp-column>\n\n <fdp-column\n  name=\"description\"\n  key=\"description\"\n  label=\"Description\">\n </fdp-column>\n</fdp-table>\n```",
